      "Delaying CT head \u2014 this is a race against time",
      "Not activating stroke team early (call before patient arrives if possible)",
      "Treating blood pressure too aggressively before tPA (permissive HTN <220/120)",
      "Missing last-known-well time vs symptom discovery time",
      "Not considering thrombectomy for LVO \u2014 even outside tPA window"
