      "Invasive fungal infection (if fever persists >4-7 days on antibiotics \u2014 add antifungal coverage)",
      "Central line infection (if applicable \u2014 must draw cultures through line AND peripherally)",
      "Pneumocystis pneumonia (if on chronic steroids or prolonged immunosuppression without prophylaxis)"
