      "AFib in thyroid storm: rate control with beta-blocker first; cardioversion often fails until euthyroid",
      "Mortality of untreated thyroid storm is >90%; even with treatment, mortality is 10-30%",
      "Identify and treat the precipitant \u2014 in this case: medication non-compliance + dental procedure stress"
