      "Using vasopressors that worsen limb ischemia (norepinephrine) \u2014 optimize cardiac output instead",
      "Not preparing for reperfusion syndrome \u2014 hyperkalemia, acidosis, and myoglobin washout can be lethal",
      "Assuming chronic PAD \u2014 sudden onset with no prior claudication in a patient with AFib = embolic until proven otherwise"
