      "Not obtaining CT with IV contrast \u2014 you need to assess bowel wall enhancement to detect ischemia",
      "Relying on a single lactate \u2014 trend the lactate; a rising lactate indicates progression",
      "Not placing an NG tube early \u2014 decompression reduces vomiting, aspiration risk, and may resolve partial obstruction",
      "Missing the transition from 'watchful waiting' to surgical emergency \u2014 serial abdominal exams every 4-6 hours",
      "Correcting metabolic alkalosis with NS alone \u2014 need to replace chloride AND potassium (KCl in IVF)"
