          "name": "Emergent Pericardiocentesis (echo-guided)",
          "correct": true,
          "group": "Critical",
          "critical": true,
          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Definitive treatment. Even 30-50mL removal dramatically improves hemodynamics. Leave drain.",
