      "Hypervolemia/pulmonary edema (missed dialysis = fluid overload \u2014 may need emergent dialysis for both K and volume)",
      "Medication contribution (stop ACE-I and spironolactone \u2014 both potassium-retaining in ESRD)",
      "Concurrent metabolic acidosis (bicarb 14 \u2014 acidosis drives potassium extracellularly; correction helps lower K)"
