          "teaching": "Ketorolac 15\u201330 mg IV is an effective NSAID for acute migraine that inhibits prostaglandin-mediated neurogenic inflammation and central sensitization. It can be used as monotherapy or combined synergistically with a dopamine antagonist (prochlorperazine or metoclopramide) for refractory cases. Avoid in patients with renal impairment or GI bleeding history.",
