          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Acyclovir (400 mg five times daily x5\u20137 days) or valacyclovir (1g BID x7\u201310 days) treats active HSV infection and shortens the EM episode duration by eliminating the antigenic stimulus driving the hypersensitivity reaction. In recurrent HSV-triggered EM (\u22653 episodes/year), long-term suppressive antiviral therapy (acyclovir 400 mg BID or valacyclovir 500 mg daily) prevents both HSV recurrence and EM flares.",
