          "name": "Increase topical steroid potency \u2014 worsening eczema flare",
          "correct": false,
          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Increasing topical corticosteroid potency in eczema herpeticum will dramatically worsen the HSV infection. Topical steroids suppress local immune surveillance, promote viral replication, and accelerate HSV dissemination across already-compromised eczematous skin. This is a life-threatening error \u2014 eczema herpeticum requires immediate IV acyclovir and complete cessation of topical steroids on infected areas, not escalation of immunosuppressive therapy.",
