          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Chronic FPIES frequently causes failure to thrive from protein-energy malnutrition, fat malabsorption, and micronutrient deficiencies due to chronic intestinal inflammation. After eliminating the trigger protein, close nutritional monitoring \u2014 weekly weight checks initially \u2014 confirms recovery. Dietitian involvement ensures adequate caloric density and micronutrient repletion in the transition to hypoallergenic formula.",
