          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Establish tissue diagnosis before starting steroids or radiation \u2014 treatment obscures pathology. Bronchoscopy, CT-guided biopsy, or mediastinoscopy. Exception: life-threatening SVC syndrome (stridor, AMS, severe hypoxia) = treat empirically, biopsy later. The underlying malignancy type determines definitive treatment.",
