          "name": "Physical restraints for confused patient safety",
          "group": "Restraints",
          "critical": false,
          "correct": false,
          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Restraints WORSEN delirium \u2014 increase agitation, cause aspiration/pressure ulcers/falls, and prolong hospital stay. Avoid unless immediate safety risk. Structured sitter, family, or mitts are preferable alternatives.",
