          "phase": 1,
          "teaching": "Takotsubo (stress cardiomyopathy) echo: apical ballooning with basal hyperkinesis \u2014 pattern extends beyond a single coronary territory. This is pathognomonic and distinguishes Takotsubo from ACS (which follows a coronary distribution). Modified Mayo Criteria: apical ballooning + no obstructive CAD + ECG changes + no pheochromocytoma/myocarditis.",
