          "teaching": "Contact lenses must be DISCONTINUED immediately and not resumed until fully healed (weeks) and ophthalmologist clearance. Contact lens worn during active infection introduces new organisms and disrupts corneal epithelial healing. Discard all contact lenses and cases worn during the illness.",
