          "group": "Surgical",
          "critical": false,
          "correct": true,
          "phase": 2,
          "teaching": "Second-look laparotomy planned at 24h if bowel viability was uncertain at initial surgery \u2014 some ischemic-appearing bowel may recover with revascularization. Avoids unnecessary resection of potentially viable bowel while preventing contamination from missed necrosis. Coordinate with surgical team.",
