          "teaching": "Antigen avoidance is the cornerstone of HP management \u2014 the single most important intervention. Identify through detailed exposure history: farmer's lung (thermophilic actinomycetes), bird fancier's lung (avian proteins), hot tub lung (mycobacteria), humidifier fever. Complete permanent avoidance is required to halt progression.",
