          "teaching": "BiPAP for concurrent COPD exacerbation with hypercapnic failure \u2014 reduces intubation and mortality. Target SpO2 88-92%. Reassess at 1-2h: if pH <7.25 or declining GCS, intubate. BiPAP does not treat the pneumonia but manages the respiratory failure.",
