          "teaching": "Anti-CCP is the most specific test for RA (95% specificity) and predicts erosive, more severe disease. RF is less specific (also positive in Sj\u00f6gren, SLE, infections). DAS28 or CDAI to quantify disease activity at baseline and follow-up. Baseline X-rays hands/feet + CXR before starting biologics.",
